Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HaiSai（你好呀）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是聯絡板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等我就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？這本雜誌下期會做湯乃鷺溫泉的特輯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是也有這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗訪調查排行榜？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的從業人員都很關注那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位居排行榜前列的話  客人的預約果然就會多起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有效果的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我們喜翠莊也得加把勁才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人來取材拍我的照片的話  該怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是去一趟美容院的好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能順利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在少爺到現在為止做過的事情裡  這也是最差勁的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼  首先宣傳總是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（免費住宿券  一夜兩餐）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是崇子小姐教我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是很閒的話就來幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出我很閒是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為大好週末就只有一組客人光顧的緣故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦…  優惠券
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  這裡是喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一直以來都承蒙您關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  是兩位對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  恭候您大駕光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常客辻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真夠走運的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  這裡是喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  真是非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是預約今天的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是有幾位呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見呢  你特意跑出來買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為客人好像突然多起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那我來幫你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  不用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次湯乃鷺要在雜誌上出一期特輯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  那個排行榜的編排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就是最近一陣完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  要是喜翠莊勇奪榜首 客源不斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定不得了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣的話  老闆娘那張總板著的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會變得笑瞇瞇的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  你們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止都幹得都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家接下來就慢慢玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就去泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就吃好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就玩抽烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽烏龜～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這和平時也沒什麼大區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊  休息的是小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加許多人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有七組  共計二十人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常客們和心血來潮的客人撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們還有房間空著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能謝絕別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不能給客人提供滿意的服務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絕客人也是我們分內之事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你通知過蓮先生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然徹君今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就人數來看應該還不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  沒法克服的問題看來就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  這麼多人就靠我和緒花的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙不過來的時候  我也會來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前可也是位女服務員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘看起來好像挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～啊  我也好想要個休息天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民沒休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好認真…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想快點熟悉工作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在休息天裡也拼命幹活的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹先生肯定也會感動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒準就喜歡上小民了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我剛才是不是又毛蛋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爺  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每次說起這個你都跑那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘  老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去喊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘  您不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要大聲呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘的病情近期明明已經穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老毛病了  雖然應該沒什麼大礙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺不一起跟著去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然老闆娘不在  我又怎麼能請假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說今天還會來許多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種時候  我更要加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才像是少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂喂  崇子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十萬夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是四十萬翠夫人的親人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上會再做一次檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人喊四十萬夫人我都沒注意到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  老闆娘是我的外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回到工作崗位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人突然就多起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在人手不夠  工作應該很緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您自己身體的問題也很緊張呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了我這年紀  身上總會有一兩個毛病的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也不能因為這樣就不叫救護車呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是救護車來了  你說客人們會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是客人客人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您除了客人就不想些別的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份工作就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會再來探望您了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套我本來剛想去取的帳本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了你快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  拜託你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是皋月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…嗶…的一聲提示音之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就麻煩你在20秒以內  做·個·留·言·哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  外婆她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟阿孝打電話  我又能說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是緒花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  聲音好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  這算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  緒花  我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在開往你那邊的列車上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？  什麼？  剛才我沒聽清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在人在列車上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  是要去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝剛才好像說要來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麻煩你把茶點送去藤之間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  恕我失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行重要的任務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花也回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起聽一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才需要brainstorming
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,brain…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我也還有工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小說家為目標的這15年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸磨練出來的觀察力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於派上用處了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吹了  快說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之可疑的是月之間的兩位女性顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有波之間的一位男性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標必定是這兩組其中之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗訪記者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗訪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種淡季突然增加來客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面一定存在Reason
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說此刻喜翠莊中一定存在著雜誌的暗訪記者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time like the present（機不可失  失不再來）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把握此刻Chance不會自己送上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出暗訪記者  並給予重點服務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後成功Get排行榜榜首
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說要區別對待顧客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course  當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…其他顧客的招待要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他顧客當然是給予與以往相同的稱心服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之上給暗訪記者重點服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃分工作優先順序對專業人士來說是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情用事太過天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花  這是讓我們重整旗鼓的絕好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老闆娘的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點根據我的計劃開始行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次郎也去準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你催
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帶我去廚房嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用晚餐決勝負？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是讓我們給那些有可能是暗訪記者的人開小灶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以食開始  以食結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民以食為天！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的晚餐正是喜翠莊的Critical Time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕不能輸的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！今晚的Dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而烹製的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐決勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手滑了而已喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這個深受好評
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時期的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心就去看望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做的話反而會被老闆娘斥責的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這種繁忙時刻搞什麼呢」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在醫院的時候  被老闆娘拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來她說房間有本帳本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就交給我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  豆丁老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是帳本…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那麼詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這個地方的人都這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個顧客的情況都寫得那麼詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吉先生是幾點入住來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生的情況有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像和平時有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真是出人意外的經不起壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話就趕不上所有人份的晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先那兩組人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  別無他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是最佳方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒其他辦法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做的話絕對會被老闆娘斥責的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直就是這麼被老闆娘斥責過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧客都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情應該是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是緒花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手也不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間也很緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫了幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說是「不好了  拜託了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是要出席婚禮出城了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先聯繫看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我就打過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打過了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說一直在廚房打下手 但料理我還什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜這個拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有借我自行車鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民沒關係的  我去叫徹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…毛蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我所能做的事  必須做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是按照自己的想法在行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老闆娘不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有些不安呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  請再多等我一會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  不知道徹先生在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  只有一間間找過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花  你現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我來做  請讓我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}男人的腦袋的氣味是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝  真的  真的謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
